trans-unit.source: Defines the methods that enable a client application to display a user interface to collect identity information prior to creating the channel.
trans-unit.target: Definierar metoder som gör att ett klientprogram att visa ett användargränssnitt för att samla in information om identitet innan du skapar kanalen.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IInteractiveChannelInitializer interface to enable a client application to display a user interface that enables the user of the application to create or select the credentials prior to opening a channel.
trans-unit.target: Implementera gränssnittet IInteractiveChannelInitializer om du vill aktivera ett klientprogram att visa ett användargränssnitt som gör att användaren av programmet kan skapa eller välj autentiseringsuppgifterna före öppna en kanal.

trans-unit.source: To implement IInteractiveChannelInitializer, perform the following steps in <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInteractiveChannelInitializer.BeginDisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>: 1.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill implementera IInteractiveChannelInitializer, utför följande steg i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInteractiveChannelInitializer.BeginDisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>: 1.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInteractiveChannelInitializer.BeginDisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Prompt the user and obtain an appropriate <xref:System.Net.NetworkCredential?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Fråga användaren och hämta ett lämpligt <xref:System.Net.NetworkCredential?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Net.NetworkCredential?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Add a custom channel parameter object to the collection returned by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannel.GetProperty%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> object with a type parameter of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ChannelParameterCollection?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Lägg till en anpassad kanal parameter-objekt i samlingen som returneras av- <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannel.GetProperty%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden på <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel>objekt med en parameter av typen av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ChannelParameterCollection?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ChannelParameterCollection?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannel.GetProperty%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This channel parameter object is used by the custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientCredentialsSecurityTokenManager?displayProperty=fullName> to establish the security tokens for the channel.
trans-unit.target: Den här kanalen parameter-objekt används av ett anpassat <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientCredentialsSecurityTokenManager?displayProperty=fullName>upprätta säkerhetstoken för kanalen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientCredentialsSecurityTokenManager?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Return.
trans-unit.target: Returnera.

trans-unit.source: To insert IInteractiveChannelInitializer: 1.
trans-unit.target: Infoga IInteractiveChannelInitializer: 1.

trans-unit.source: Override the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.ApplyClientBehavior%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials?displayProperty=fullName> class.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosätt <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.ApplyClientBehavior%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials?displayProperty=fullName>klassen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.ApplyClientBehavior%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In that method, determine whether the endpoint requires an IInteractiveChannelInitializer and if so, add the IInteractiveChannelInitializer to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientRuntime.InteractiveChannelInitializers%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden, avgör om slutpunkten kräver en IInteractiveChannelInitializer och i så fall, lägga till IInteractiveChannelInitializer till den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientRuntime.InteractiveChannelInitializers%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samling.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ClientRuntime.InteractiveChannelInitializers%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: There are two ways application developers can make use of an inserted IInteractiveChannelInitializer.
trans-unit.target: Det finns två sätt som programutvecklare kan utnyttja en infogad IInteractiveChannelInitializer.

trans-unit.source: The client application can call either <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> (or an asynchronous version) prior to opening the channel (the *explicit* approach) or simply call the first operation (the *implicit* approach).
trans-unit.target: Klientprogrammet kan anropa antingen <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>(eller en asynkron version) innan öppning av kanalen (den *explicit* metod) eller anropa bara den första åtgärden (den *implicit* metod).</xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If using the implicit approach, the application must call the first operation on an <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> extension.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder metoden implicit programmet måste anropa den första åtgärden för en <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel>tillägget.</xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601>

trans-unit.source: If it calls anything other than the first operation, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Om något annat än den första åtgärden anropas, genereras ett undantag.

trans-unit.source: If using the explicit approach, the application must perform the following steps in order: 1.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder metoden explicit programmet måste göra följande i ordning: 1.

trans-unit.source: Call either <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> (or an asynchronous version).
trans-unit.target: Anropa antingen <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>(eller en asynkron version).</xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.DisplayInitializationUI%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When the initializers have returned, call either the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ICommunicationObject.Open%2A> method on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> object or on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> object returned from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.InnerChannel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: När initierarna ha returnerat anropa antingen den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ICommunicationObject.Open%2A>metoden på den <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel>objekt eller på den <xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel>objektet som returneras från den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.InnerChannel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.InnerChannel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> </xref:System.ServiceModel.IClientChannel> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ICommunicationObject.Open%2A>

trans-unit.source: Call operations.
trans-unit.target: Anropa åtgärder.

trans-unit.source: It is recommended that production-quality applications control of the user-interface process by adopting the explicit approach.
trans-unit.target: Det rekommenderas hög kvalitet program kontrollen processens användargränssnittet genom att explicit metod.

trans-unit.source: Applications that use the implicit approach invoke the user-interface initializers, but if the user of the application fails to respond within the send timeout period of the binding, an exception is thrown when the user interface returns.
trans-unit.target: Program som använder den implicita metoden anropa användargränssnittet initierare, men om användaren om programmet inte svarar inom tidsgränsen för send för bindningen, genereras ett undantag när användargränssnittet returnerar.

trans-unit.source: An asynchronous call to begin using a user interface to obtain credential information.
trans-unit.target: Ett asynkront anrop kan börja använda ett användargränssnitt för att hämta information om autentiseringsuppgifter.
